My Intensive Care is soon to be called Eolas Medical! With increasing demand from people in other specialities, we're moving under one app to be able to offer our platform to everyone.

My Intensive Care is a platform that allows departments to have single source of truth for all their content, everything from guidelines and education to checklists and staff alerts.
